P_matrix: the camera 

last_lower_bounding_box: lower bounding of box for point cloud selection
last_upper_bounding_box: upper bounding of box for point cloud selection
bounding_box_extend: the extension of the bounding of box

sor.setLeafSize(0.02f, 0.02f, 0.02f): Voxel Grid filter leaf size

Default value of depth difference in Eq. (7): 0.02 (cdcpd.cpp L221)

initial_sigma_scale: 1/8

lambda: start_lambda * std::pow(annealing_factor, iterations + 1) (in Eq. (18))
start_lambda = 1.0
annealing factor = 0.6

alpha: 3.0

lle_neighbors = 8; // parameter for lle calculation
